    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior shows extensive wear, including large dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust on the rocker panels. Mechanically, the engine runs very roughly and the transmission frequently slips, making it unreliable for daily use. The interior has torn upholstery and several non-functional electronics. This is a project car or parts donor and is sold strictly as-is; please bring a trailer.",
