      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional vehicle maintained to the highest possible standards. This specimen exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, reflecting a history of uncompromising care. With zero compromises in its presentation or performance, this unit represents a premier acquisition for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
